  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The expression above is equivalent to <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, x squared, plus b x, plus c \"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">a</span>, <span class=\"italic\">b</span>, and <span class=\"italic\">c</span> are constants. What is the value of <span class=\"italic\">b</span>?</p>\n",
